Name: Sacred Salt
AttributesDescription: An item that Butler the Steward of the Order at the Supply Station is collecting and willing to trade for.
BgDescription: To the Acolytes, Sacred Salt has the ability to cleanse anything untouched by the Sentinel's grace. With its purifying power, sliced bread turns into the Divinity's nurturing meal, ordinary wine becomes holy blood that grants enlightenment...
AccessDescriptions: Fabricatorium of the Deep Exploration Progress Reward
